(OCDAO), will develop JS workflow automation, business intelligence, and AI applications to achieve decision advantage. This
includes developing and testing JS-specific software applications or use cases to support the Chairman’s statutory responsibility
to provide military advice to the President, the National Security Council, the Homeland Security Council, and the Secretary of
