-- Inform the development, design and assessment of updates to Missile Defense architecture.
-- Identify architecture alternatives that improve Missile Defense System performance and are complementary to and
interoperable with NATO systems and theaters around the world.
-- Lead collaborative effort to improve foreign partners' understanding of Missile Defense System capabilities and architectural
