Description: Develop, procure, deliver, and integrate distributed land-based radar capability for use in acquiring, tracking,
identifying, and discriminating threats to Guam, including the necessary on-island support equipment for power, data
communications to AGS, cooling, and environmental protection. Provide transportation, delivery, integration, testing, operations,
and limited spares. Planned activities include:
