missiles in an ashore configuration. Aegis Ashore provides sophisticated engagement strategies and can adapt to threat updates within each site's designated area of
responsibility. Aegis Ashore re-hosts the required BMD components of a U.S. Navy Destroyer, including:

- Army/Navy Surface Radar Surveillance and Control Radar.
