D. Acquisition Strategy
Aegis Ashore primarily achieves the cybersecurity mission through Other Government Agencies Statements of Work with Naval Information Warfare Command Pacific
and Naval Surface Warfare Center Philadelphia, to implement cybersecurity best practices, assist with authorizations to connect and operate connected systems, install
system patches and upgrade software, support cyber testing and analysis, and ensuring mandatory cyber clauses are included and enforced on contracts.




